==Korean==

===Verb===
'''날다''' nal-da (present form: 날아 nal-a)
# to [[fly]] (travel through the air)
#:종이 비행기가 아주 멋지게 '''난다''' (''Jongi bihaengi-ga aju meotjige '''nanda''''') The paper airplane '''flies''' really splendidly.
# (of a color or scent) to [[fade]]
#:청바지를 자주 빨아 색이 '''날았다'''. (''Cheongbajireul jaju bbara saegi '''narattda''''') The jeans were washed so often the color '''faded'''. 
